1
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,720
What's wrong?

2
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,200
Is your father sick again?

3
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,000
No.

4
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,720
It's my Second Uncle. He's dying.

5
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,800
Lead the way, quickly.

6
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:23,640
Let's go.

7
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,800
Okay, hurry up.

8
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,920
It's this kid.

9
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:40,320
It's too early to talk about death.

10
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:41,360
He can still be saved.

11
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,120
Let me see.

12
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,160
Hey.

13
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,800
Where did this woman come from?

14
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,039
Don't touch my brother.

15
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,520
Who knows what you plan to do to him?

16
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,080
Huh?

17
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,960
Blocking someone from saving your brother like this,

18
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,039
could it be that

19
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,860
you don't want him to survive?

20
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,920
Didn't you say

21
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,360
that while Old Hu was sick,

22
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:59,160
he wanted to fight for the inheritance?

23
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,560
Why are you suddenly here?

24
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,220
It's because we suspected him

25
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,120
so

26
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:05,200
we planned to report him to the officials.

27
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,720
Right.

28
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:06,480
I don't know.

29
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,240
How did he suddenly get the news

30
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,000
and come running to tell us he had his reasons?

31
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,000
Let me see.

32
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,600
What reasons?

33
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:19,730
Not sure.

34
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:22,490
He fell unconscious just as he was about to speak.

35
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,060
Poisonous insects again.

36
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,360
Shen Yi.

37
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,600
Give me the tools.

38
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:03,840
Shen Yi.

39
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,560
Scissors.

40
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:08,920
Shen Yi.

41
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:09,720
Master Shen.

42
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,280
Master.

43
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,060
Shen Yi.

44
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:18,720
Jiujiu.

45
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,720
You fainted just now.

46
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,520
How do you feel?

47
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,720
Ji Bai.

48
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,280
I...

49
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,760
What happened to me?

50
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,520
How is Miss Hu's second uncle?

51
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,360
He's fine.

52
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,920
You can't stand blood.

53
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,640
You passed out when you saw it.

54
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,680
How are you feeling?

55
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,760
Ji Bai.

56
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,880
Am I the Jiujiu you're looking for?

57
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,000
Why do you say that?

58
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,560
I had a very long dream.

59
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:12,240
I called your name in it.

60
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,360
And I dreamt you called me Jiujiu.

61
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,079
Maybe.

62
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:23,240
You've confused dreams with reality.

63
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,120
You got them mixed up.

64
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,460
But those scenes felt so real.

65
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,720
I don't think they were just dreams.

66
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,380
They might be my memories.

67
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,800
Since you faint at the sight of blood,

68
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,860
you should stop roaming the Jianghu.

69
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:44,240
I'll send word to the Zhenbei Prince's Mansion

70
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,800
to have someone pick you up.

71
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,000
I won't go back.

72
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,420
You have no choice.

73
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,120
What's wrong with her?

74
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,640
Is it because I fainted

75
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,490
that she is concerned about me?

76
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,920
Young brother,

77
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,960
I am the Head Escort of the Yan Family Escort Agency.

78
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,440
If you need anything,

79
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:20,320
feel free to find me at the Yan Family Escort Agency.

80
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,720
General Shen.

81
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,280
Jiujiu.

82
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,800
Yan Family Escort Agency.

83
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,820
What exactly does this have to do with me?

84
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,120
Is what I'm doing

85
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,200
unfair to him?

86
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,520
Since he has forgotten,

87
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,560
it's best not to remember.

88
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,640
Perhaps for him,

89
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,050
this is the best choice.

90
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,920
Please deliver this letter

91
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:16,180
to Zhenbei Prince's Manor immediately.

92
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,560
Strange.

93
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,160
Where did Ji Bai go?

94
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,600
General.

95
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,800
General.

96
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,000
General?

97
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:34,480
The General you mentioned,

98
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,610
is his surname Shen?

99
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:37,290
You know about the General.

100
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,760
You must be the lost Young Master.

101
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,659
You look just like the General

102
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,560
when he was young.

103
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,720
Do you know

104
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:47,860
how hard we've searched for you all these years?

105
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:50,920
Sir,

106
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,600
let's talk.

107
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,640
Okay.

108
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,600
Young Master,

109
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,159
I

110
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:57,040
have so much to tell you.

111
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:12,080
Why hasn't Xiao Heyan come back yet?

112
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:15,160
I need to go find him.

113
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:22,320
Where have you been?

114
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,400
Ji Bai.

115
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,100
Are you hiding something from me?

116
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,120
You're overthinking it.

117
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,120
Stop pretending.

118
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,520
I know everything.

119
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,360
I'm the Jiu Jiu you're looking for,

120
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,690
General Shen's orphan.

121
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,920
Right?

122
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,440
What nonsense are you talking about?

123
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,680
You are the Heir of the Prince of Zhenbei.

124
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,520
Where did you hear that?

125
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,560
Don't worry about that.

126
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,480
I have my ways.

127
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:54,840
Just tell me,

128
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,080
was what I said right?

129
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,520
I don't know.

130
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,840
What exactly are you avoiding?

131
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,370
I'm not avoiding anything.

132
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:05,960
I told you,

133
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,480
you're overthinking it.

134
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,880
You and Jiujiu

135
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:11,090
have nothing to do with each other.

136
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,280
Doctor Ji.

137
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,000
I just...

138
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,970
thought I heard you arguing with Master Shen.

139
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,640
It's nothing.

140
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,280
Go back and rest.

141
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,679
Doctor Ji.

142
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,600
Just now,

143
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:48,340
what were you and Master Shen arguing about?

144
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,720
About his origins.

145
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,960
What about his origins?

146
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:00,880
He...

147
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:04,960
I can't...

148
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,040
Is there something

149
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,900
you're keeping from Master Shen?

150
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:12,180
Something you're afraid he'll find out?

151
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:16,000
I killed his mother.

152
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,440
Chuyun.

153
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,400
Why are you here?

154
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,360
I saw you arguing just now,

155
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,600
so I came out to check.

156
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,720
What happened?

157
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:39,960
Arguing?

158
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:46,200
We just had a small disagreement.

159
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,200
But it's nothing serious.

160
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,680
Mhm.

161
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,920
Are you going to look for him now?

162
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:53,400
Yes.

163
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,280
Go back and get some rest.

164
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,560
Mhm.

165
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,840
Be careful.

166
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:16,760
Mr. Shen.

167
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:19,000
Are you alright?

168
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,480
You look

169
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,560
really pale.

170
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,960
You suddenly fainted today.

171
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,960
I was so worried.

172
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,440
It's nothing.

173
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,240
That's good.

174
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:38,120
Why does seeing them together

175
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:40,440
make me feel uneasy?

176
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,800
Am I sick?

177
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,900
Young Master Shen,

178
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,000
you're drinking alone here.

179
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:52,260
Why didn't Physician Ji come to look for you?

180
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,920
Did you quarrel?

181
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,360
Physician Ji

182
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,360
is ambitious

183
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:04,560
and wants to practice medicine to help people.

184
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,760
I'm afraid

185
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,970
she won't be willing

186
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,620
to settle down as a housewife.

187
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,760
Master Shen.

188
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,450
I may not know medicine,

189
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:23,240
but I'm good at managing a household.

190
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,800
I can take good care of you.

191
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,240
How about we run a restaurant together?

192
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,160
Stop talking.

193
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,840
Ji Bai is my wife.

194
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,040
I will only marry her.

195
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,760
If she wants to open a clinic,

196
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:34,930
I will be by her side.

197
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,760
If she wants to roam the world,

198
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:37,960
I will lead her horse.

199
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,760
If she doesn't want to be bound by marriage

200
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,280
and doesn't want to marry me,

201
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:44,480
I will follow her for the rest of my life.

202
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:45,720
Miss Hu.

203
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,960
I understand your feelings,

204
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,360
but I cannot accept them.

205
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:50,960
I'm sorry.

206
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,560
All right.

207
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,600
I understand.

208
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,200
Then I wish you

209
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:11,650
a long life together

210
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:13,120
and a happy marriage.

211
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:17,120
I won't mention this again.

212
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:25,960
You will surely find someone who loves you deeply.

213
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:33,050
Get me two jars of fine wine.

214
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,000
Okay.

215
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:46,640
Brother Shen, you honor me with your visit tonight.

216
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,800
I'm truly flattered.

217
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,770
I only know you and Ji Bai in Sitai Town.

218
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,700
We're acquaintances.

219
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,220
Let's have a drink.

220
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,800
You've never liked me, Brother Shen.

221
00:12:57,800 --> 00:13:00,240
But tonight you suddenly asked me for a drink.

222
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,500
Something must be weighing on your mind.

223
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:05,920
Don't ask.

224
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,800
Just drink.

225
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:09,940
Cheers.

226
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,680
Benefactor,

227
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:22,000
I just learned some big news.

228
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,160
Lady Chuyun,

229
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:25,000
why have you come alone?

230
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,800
As soon as I heard the news,

231
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,320
I rushed over to find you.

232
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,800
Physician Ji told me

233
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,720
she killed Master Shen's mother years ago.

234
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,240
I can't believe

235
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,720
Physician Ji is actually a murderer.

236
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:14,480
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

237
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:13,920
Yi Yinan.

238
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:14,520
Xiaoxiaoxue.

239
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,120
Xiaoxiao.

240
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,960
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

241
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,040
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

242
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:49,080
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng,

243
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:49,080
Xiulong.

244
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,010
Lyu, Sun, Zhang.

245
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:52,920
Xu.
